'''Senate Guard [[Analysis droid/Legends|analysis droids]]''' were [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]]-equipped units that analyzed evidence gathered by the [[Senate Guard/Legends|Senate Guard]] in investigations. The droids had a [[Holoprojector/Legends|Holoprojector]]. They were programmed to release sensitive information only to individuals with appropriate-level clearance. One such droid assisted [[Sagoro Autem]] in analyzing the device [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Tsian]] used to control [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droids]].

